title: Full Show (Brady vs Mahomes, Dak eyeing Week 5 return, Zion “dominated” scrimmage)
description:
00:00 Mahomes and Brady face off for 6th game. Who would you rather have on your team right now?
25:21 Dak eyeing a Week 5 return. Does Cooper Rush make it a QB controversy if he wins his third straight?
56:34 USA Today released “NFL Coaches Project” focused on analyzing demographic data of coaches
1:10:20 Nets HC Steve Nash says he doesn’t care if Ben Simmons ever shoots a jump shot
1:20:23 Belichick says “day by day” 12 times when addressing Mac Jones injury
1:30:54 Tua and the undefeated Dolphins take on Burrow and the Bengals on TNF
1:40:35 Does Mike McCarthy Football deserve credit for the Cowboys wins in Dak's absence?
1:50:03 Zion Williamson "dominated" in first scrimmage since 2020
1:54:56 LeBron becomes owner of Major League Pickleball team
